_IntegrationMaterializedLimitFailsClearly` to use `Force: true` to force the materialized path (it previously relied on no-thin to do that).\n\n## End-to-end picture\n\nFor your `--tags` sync against the artifacts target, the planner will now:\n- Detect `main` already current → skipped, not in pushPlans.\n- Detect all the new branches → `ActionCreate` plans, eligible for incremental relay.\n- Detect new tags → `ActionCreate` plans, eligible for incremental relay (already were).\n- All plans eligible → incremental relay path → source streams a pack with target refs as haves → target receive-pack accepts.\n\nAvoids the materialized-walker rabbit hole entirely. Worth re-running:\n\n```sh\nGODEBUG=http2client=0 go run cmd/git-sync/main.go sync --tags \\\n  https://github.com/entireio/cli.git $ARTIFACTS_REMOTE\n```\n\nExpect either success or, if there's a separate server-side issue, an error from a much cleaner code path that we can diagnose more directly."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":631,"cache_read_input_tokens":220053,"output_tokens":1087,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":631,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":1087,"cache_read_input_tokens":220053,"cache_creation_input_tokens":631,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":631},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011Cag1xRohYk4HfUStHoPaJ","type":"assistant","uuid":"a8746bd0-84a1-4906-afd5-ac24b33772ad","timestamp":"2026-05-03T17:19:09.351Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/git-sync","sessionId":"124cf89f-b950-42d0-8c90-1990b889f0bc","version":"2.1.123","gitBranch":"main"}
